NOTE: Should be ran with OPA version 1.1.0 or higher!
NOTE: The versions on the homepage of opalang are not up to date at all and if you're unlucky you probably need to build it yourself to get the latest.

Once you got it the following commands in terminal:
> opa ace/ace.js ace/ace.opa jquery-ui/widgets.js jquery-ui/widgets.opa --opx-dir _build --import-package stdlib.database.mongo    --conf opa.conf --conf-opa-files -o dopa.exe --build-dir _build/dopa.exe
> ./dopa.exe